QUICKSTART

Setup compilation environment:

    $ cd makl && make hints

    [ set MAKEFLAGS and MAKL_DIR as suggested ]

    $ make toolchain
    $ cd ..

Configure, make and install KLone:

    $ ./configure && make depend && make
    $ sudo make install

Import the example web-application

    $ cd site && klone -c import ../doc/example-site
    $ cd .. && make

Launch the KLone executable:

    $ ./src/kloned/kloned

Start your web browser:

    [ start your web browser and go to http://localhost:4567/ ]

For further info and documentation:
    http://www.koanlogic.com/
